{"tid":2285633,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"藝術應唔應該成為抗爭工具？","createTime":"2020-11-14T09:19:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-14T10:57:38.000Z","uid":303833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"fc0780b1f2bf1719d12a9be8ec9b11ab906c7996","tid":2285633,"uid":303833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T09:19:58.000Z","msg":"有一派話政治唔應該綁架藝術<br />\n有一派話藝術架應該要有社會擔當<br />\n<br />\n金馬獎風波「日前更傳出中國當局下達禁令，將不再允許中資影片報名金馬獎。對於此一軒然大波，台灣影界人士議論紛紛，其中不乏持「政治歸政治，藝術歸藝術」論調者，企圖檢討獲獎者發言，認為不該讓影視界沾染上如此濃厚的「政治」色彩，致使如今兩岸可能失去珍貴交流機會。」<br />\n<br />\n如果藝術成為政治宣傳嘅工具，咁仲值唔值得我地欣賞；又或者一個避政治不談嘅藝術家，好似王菀之咁，佢嘅作品仲有何深度<br />\n<br />\n大家討論下"},{"pid":"8dfd696c68c6ffbe015853970285951cd2081c1e","tid":2285633,"uid":201604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T09:21:06.000Z","msg":"唔好將xx政治化"},{"pid":"4c859fcdbc7b1e3851daec850b5b6cb6218eacc3","tid":2285633,"uid":303833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T09:21:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f3be064eb1d822aad6cc89b53857ee92f68c9b3d","tid":2285633,"uid":147782,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T09:22:12.000Z","msg":"好難分得開"},{"pid":"a4e8e19f508f7607090955629ccad7ecd3a451de","tid":2285633,"uid":303833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8dfd696c68c6ffbe015853970285951cd2081c1e","tid":2285633,"uid":201604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T09:21:06.000Z","msg":"唔好將xx政治化"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T09:22:18.000Z","msg":"但係好對藝術家都視反映社會現況 改變社會係自己嘅責任"},{"pid":"96d486ba3fec7c85fd53f383bd37cf2664ceb2aa","tid":2285633,"uid":43575,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T09:22:22.000Z","msg":"自己功課自己做啦"},{"pid":"7e584cf2b85b3030d827f3faad89935604a822bd","tid":2285633,"uid":201604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a4e8e19f508f7607090955629ccad7ecd3a451de","tid":2285633,"uid":303833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8dfd696c68c6ffbe015853970285951cd2081c1